ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE: UPDATE GROSS_MARGIN A SET GROSS_MARGIN_IND = 'N' WHERE A.SLBA_DIVISION_CODE='SC' AND ( A.SALES_MEASURE_NAME in ('Devel Fund', 'Perm Price', 'Temp Price', 'Cons Promo', 'Coop') or ( A.COST_MEASURE_NAME = 'Sales Incent' and a.charge_allowance_prefix_desc<>'F' ) ) and update_userid not like '%SAP%' and A.FISCAL_YEAR = (select to_number(d.cy_year_yyyy) from day_dimension d where d.day_date=trunc(sysdate)) and A.FISCAL_PERIOD=(select to_number(d.cy_month_num) from day_dimension d where d.day_date=trunc(sysdate));

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SAS935WX.SAPRM#, SAS935WX.SABCLA, SAS935WX.SAGROS, SAS935WX.SARETR, SAS935WX.SAUNAL, SAS935WX.SAMARK, SAS935WX.SADIST, SAS935WX.SAOTH, SAS935WX.SACOG, SAS935WX.SAPRS, SAS935WX.SAUNT, SAS935WX.SADRC, SUBSTR(LTRIM(RTRIM(SAS935WX.SAPN)),1,10), SAS935WX.SAWH, SUBSTR(LTRIM(RTRIM(SAS935WX.SACPN)),1,10), SAS935WX.SAOBTK, SAS935WX.SAOSTK, SAS935WX.SAORD#, SAS935WX.SASUFX, SAS935WX.SAOTYP, SAS935WX.SAINV#, SAS935WX.SABPO#, SAS935WX.SASHPD, SAS935WX.SAINVD, SAS935WX.SACBD, SAS935WX.SANBD, SAS935WX.SAGLAC, SAS935WX.SAQLTY, SAS935WX.SAREQD, SAS935WX.SAOQS, SAS935WX.SAREAS, SAS935WX.SAXCHG, SAS935WX.SACOT, SAS935WX.SADOZ, SAS935WX.SASSKU, SAS935WX.SATRGR, SAS935WX.SAGEOG, SAS935WX.SAINT, SAS935WX.SADIV,SAS935WX.SAITEM, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY saord#, SAITEM ORDER BY RRN(SAS935WX) ASC) AS RNK, '1' AS DUMMY FROM SAPRDDATA.SAS935WX SAS935WX where SAS935WX.SAPD=$$CURR_MONTH ORDER BY RRN(SAS935WX)
